    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Loose-leaf binders with either solid or sectional posts that pass through holes in the margins of the individual leaves, typically intended for pages that are unusually large and heavy, such as in a scrapbook.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
